text: allahanu, ondu udaharaneyannu niduttane; obbanu (yarado) malakatvadalliruva adhikaravillada dasanagiddane hagu innobbanige navu uttama sampattannu dayapalisiddu, avanu adarinda guttagiyu bahirangavagiyu (satkaryakke) vecca maduttane. Avarenu samanare? Prasansegalu allahanige. Adare avaralli heccinavaru aritilla
